{"tid":1007287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏] 梵蒂岡[促請中國不要利用中梵協議　強逼教徒加入愛國會","createTime":"2019-02-03T16:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T13:18:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de9bed3c5c71dfcf06442cd44ff35003904e649c","tid":1007287,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡促請中國不要利用中梵協議　強逼教徒加入愛國會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441387-20190203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441387-20190203.htm&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=a18d2f59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441387-20190203.htm&h=42f728e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441387-20190203.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n梵蒂岡萬民福音傳播部部長費洛尼樞機，接受《羅馬觀察報》訪問時，促請中國當局不要利用去年中梵簽訂的主教任命臨時協議，強逼內地天主教徒加入天主教愛國會。<br />\n<br />\n費洛尼表示，梵蒂岡並非要求中國的地下教會消失，讓位給北京認可的天主教愛國會，強調中國只有一個教會，中國天主教會經過60年的分裂和苦難，期望天主教愛國會及地下教會能達致真正合一，呼籲中國當局尊重信仰自由。"},{"pid":"22b08e4e6f3e7cd1f7fb369d4b86cd0754338b53","tid":1007287,"uid":121146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"呼籲梵蒂岡尊重中梵協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db00b2d29ee1a471da8557d2264fa63b98de1a6","tid":1007287,"uid":108467,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yq4KupF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYq4KupF.png&h=2b6bf8a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VY5hPpG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVY5hPpG.png&h=7587b974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梵蒂岡有冇出過聲？"},{"pid":"a6b9de345807f687d8c8c522bb3c52e278ebb9c1","tid":1007287,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"reply